=== Configuration ===
==== Compiler settings ====
More info is available at: 
* [[GCC optimization]]
* [[MAKEOPTS]]
* [[EMERGE_DEFAULT_OPTS]]
{{FileBox|filename=/etc/portage/make.conf|lang=bash|1=
# O2 for super-safe output
CFLAGS="-march=ivybridge -O2 -pipe"
CXXFLAGS="${CFLAGS}"
# Dual-core with enabled Hyper-Threading technology - 4 logical processors
MAKEOPTS="-j4"
# AMD64 architecture
CHOST="x86_64-pc-linux-gnu"

}}

==== Packages settings ====
For more info: [[CPU_FLAGS_X86]]
{{FileBox|filename=/etc/portage/make.conf|lang=bash|1=
# Obtained via cpuinfo2cpuflags-x86
CPU_FLAGS_X86="aes avx mmx mmxext popcnt sse sse2 sse3 sse4_1 sse4_2 ssse3"
}}

==== USE flags ====
With [[Intel|Intel Modesetting DDX]] as video driver and [[Libinput|libinput]] as input driver add the USE flags <code>glamor</code> and <code>libinput</code>.

{{FileBox|filename=/etc/portage/make.conf|lang=bash|1=
# Intel GMA Gen 7 - IvyBridge
VIDEO_CARDS="intel i965"
# Input devices
INPUT_DEVICES="libinput"
# Useflags
USE="glamor libinput"
}}

==== Utils ====
For battery charge thresholds use: {{Package|app-laptop/tpacpi-bat}}. Example econfig and instructions can be found at: [https://github.com/teleshoes/tpacpi-bat/tree/master/examples github.com/teleshoes/tpacpi-bat].

